{"tid":2513933,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"閃電11人日本最強11人（433陣式）","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T08:37:02.000Z","uid":305479,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2a11cc1523ba38d76dcf63e1fe8ddec51fa11622","tid":2513933,"uid":305479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"只係計無印版<br />\n龍門：圓堂守<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR7keek543NYdvNjnrqS49j7VoBDqQovAMVKRDDmhfDfD?filename=6zEP2mp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zEP2mp.jpg&h=3b0519da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不斷訓練，勝出日本足球拓展賽打贏外星學院最後贏埋世青杯<br />\n由單手上帝之手進化到自己既god catch，擁有無限鬥志嘅隊長<br />\n後衛：吹雪  壁山  飛鷹 木暮<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeuejqjWuaYGyu7mBNoNj7rGD9iwAps251p4vR2cvkfjK?filename=J4dAXW8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4dAXW8.gif&h=be68acd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬能後衛吹雪守又得攻又得，必要時可以代替前鋒，而且能力值高<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXp96QDwhBw8vFfQ5ViBpRxCzNDa5r9Y4WTyasLyJcsaj?filename=Hi1SfKO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHi1SfKO.gif&h=d9b9f403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壁山係全勤成員幾乎冇一場唔會出場，克服心理關口之後發揮穩定，龐大嘅身形更加有利使出必殺技<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYPNbToV7cjB2qTzKd1KddsZ7Du5xqfZAP9DHvpNKn67Z?filename=OEGnCYq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEGnCYq.gif&h=063c6dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛鷹一招真空魔打天下，以超強腳力代替防守嘅黑道<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaqszSo27bC5dfDJS5RnZzcGZPg3vH2CoYWiQ4aJExHrJ?filename=yRXuidg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRXuidg.gif&h=52d27f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細細粒但係防守能力好強嘅後衛，知名招式係旋風陣<br />\n日本有太多勁嘅中場同前鋒，以下係我個人分析，歡迎繼續討論：<br />\n中埸：風丸 不動 鬼道 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYcBMg9jDYB4Mhu4Z9gqFS71RMkpdNF4rbDadvtYjn8VQ?filename=N06yKPq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN06yKPq.gif&h=bbbea973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n能攻能守嘅速度型中場，係圓堂最初喺田徑隊挖過嚟老友，過人盤球都有一手<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRyHchP5AM6GaXkunQJK9dMbgaRD8avPuYLf1QuNCczFJ?filename=yjOtyKa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjOtyKa.gif&h=0a2f5fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真實系中場，鏟人犯規越位陷阱樣樣做齊，非常全能，但係只有同鬼道合作嘅招式<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNp2dRDjxBvzJkQwsbuyi5cxjyhFAZTykTE47SiiJTePe?filename=4ffDbwi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ffDbwi.gif&h=0f8a99f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中場司令塔，帝國學園隊長，綜合能力非常好嘅戰術大師<br />\n<br />\n前鋒：豪炎寺 基山廣 虎丸<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUbCnSLxH2X1jWufBJieZuKRJ6z3kwbJ4nQYDhh97Sp3k?filename=g3kvMXr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3kvMXr.gif&h=6c2338bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由頭踢到落尾嘅人氣前鋒，有令人出晒水嘅火系招式，但係強項唔係主動進攻而係防守反擊，靠龍門接波之後反擊入球<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbkeTuPyss76tBoozBuBTC4hUqCy1kjdPNF1FmbZDcDdB?filename=tBeAdzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBeAdzS.gif&h=d361e97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以話係日本嘅最強前鋒，一招流星劍踢足全季，到最後係唯一一個以個人新招式踢入洛可可嘅入球，宇宙系招型到爆炸<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYnXDaMRM3gBKaAxrLSsoU5zz5LZTiLw6Tzk7zw685Dbu?filename=x2rOyKV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2rOyKV.gif&h=ca6cfb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隱藏個人能力嘅小學生，日本隊年紀最小，劇中表現最強反而係解放之後同其他人合作所出嘅招式<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"f196a7eaad3c21c6f33557ced09e2af0bc3c0622","tid":2513933,"uid":8254,"like":24,"dislike":13,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得係<br />\n<br />\n                 保方<br />\n朗拿度 何守信 成龍 占士<br />\n   前田敦子 大志偉 中志偉<br />\n      方東昇 小志強"},{"pid":"588a3d3ff43eb7acec2f016040414c39f272684c","tid":2513933,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"22aa9d16f45dd324160823c46cfda7c509eb0f25","tid":2513933,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:09:31.000Z","msg":"圖就po皇帝企鵝3號<br />\n人就冇揀單眼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b985b4251692c78648e92ad1b39e8374cf0cc4","tid":2513933,"uid":153781,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"我支持柒岡"},{"pid":"252f1f254195e6ad9130b34edf7ead425efad627","tid":2513933,"uid":72759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"後衛好似土方好過木暮，同吹雪仲有合體技"},{"pid":"5c59c2c9c8420425dac68ae5b38e6fd1587d7269","tid":2513933,"uid":305479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22aa9d16f45dd324160823c46cfda7c509eb0f25","tid":2513933,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:09:31.000Z","msg":"圖就po皇帝企鵝3號<br />\n人就冇揀單眼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"單眼佬都冇入正選咁廢"},{"pid":"59591080e6e02e4cc506d5dcf57ea1ef4cda67ba","tid":2513933,"uid":9984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"係咪有個識出單車射球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97f6aeb162e97085778ee65b0f40bf97e766c6e","tid":2513933,"uid":38751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"咁岩依家viutv 每日4點播緊 <br />\n重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔知會唔會播到世界賽"},{"pid":"977f20478df7443e3b6d748aa4c24253441318ff","tid":2513933,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97f6aeb162e97085778ee65b0f40bf97e766c6e","tid":2513933,"uid":38751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"咁岩依家viutv 每日4點播緊 <br />\n重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔知會唔會播到世界賽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"有廣東話配音？"},{"pid":"84ddd9fee4d6d376845fc1fe4ac8104ec45a7076","tid":2513933,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"當打機咁最多16人名單<br />\n同埋計埋冇入國家隊/有雙重國籍<br />\n龍門一定圓堂<br />\n<br />\n後防<br />\n壁山+飛鷹 兩個勁block技 <br />\n加埋綱海護空門buff<br />\n<br />\n中場<br />\n鬼道 不動 屈必殺戰術<br />\n風丸吹雪一人打一邊翼 反正咁快 都唔驚上咗去落唔返黎<br />\n如果一定要433最多風丸吹雪是但一件踢閘位<br />\n<br />\n前鋒<br />\n豪狗+基山廣+阿風爐 日本前鋒冇人勁過呢三條友啦<br />\n<br />\n後備 <br />\n砂木沼 打龍打前都得<br />\n冰火將 話晒二季隱藏boss<br />\n一之瀨 三季去美國踢波勁到 一個人打爆成隊日本<br />\n土門 點都要執多件後防<br />\n<br />\n本身想計埋意粉個件中田英壽 不過呢件都係黎客串套嘢就唔放入去了"},{"pid":"88e143da3450cef22989e7da954cdadc3398fd56","tid":2513933,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"木暮反而唔多突出<br />\n轉綱海打閘 <br />\n左吹雪右綱海做球比前面"},{"pid":"5a43387cabe35d4f3980d3b9ddb091262ddb1206","tid":2513933,"uid":106408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"虎丸轉亞風爐<br />\n亞風爐三個字就係原因"},{"pid":"ed98d983dad0a40ea483fdd53166743632e1ccc8","tid":2513933,"uid":38751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"977f20478df7443e3b6d748aa4c24253441318ff","tid":2513933,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97f6aeb162e97085778ee65b0f40bf97e766c6e","tid":2513933,"uid":38751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"咁岩依家viutv 每日4點播緊 <br />\n重溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔知會唔會播到世界賽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"有廣東話配音？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea16270bbe52b127f9f6cac17dde5fbbf0369346","tid":2513933,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"352<br />\n如下<br />\n豪炎寺 基山<br />\n風丸 鬼道 不動  塔子 吹雪 <br />\n  壁山 飛鷹 大腳八<br />\n         圓堂<br />\n